<br>
I am currently torn between saving around 10k to purchase knotted knuckles (great stats/awesome ratio but the 27 delay seems a little slow for primary) or the scepter of mastery (13/21 1hb).  The Zekhas Katar doesn't do it for me (the 12/23 ratio is the same as the goranga--you are basically spending 6k on the proc).  The sheetmetal ulak is a nice item and affordable (around 2k) but it has a recommended level of 50.<br>
<br>
I am curious to hear what other monks (who have likely wielded one or more of these weapons) have to say.  <br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
Trakon Mistrunner<br>
f/k/a Siman<br>
